            "text": ", for their own benefit, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " Deu 11:21",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". God promises again, upon their obedience, to drive out the nations, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " Deu 11:22-25",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". A blessing and a curse is set before them, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " Deu 11:26-28",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". They are bid to bless on Mount Gerizim, but curse on Mount Ebal, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bldvs",
            "text": " Deu 11:29",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "p",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " No text from Poole on this verse. ",
            "children": []
