      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and his statutes and his judgments, and his commandments, alway; all his laws, ceremonial, judicial, and moral; and that constantly and continually, all the days of their lives. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
